    "name": "Interact with Wizard Statue",
    "sceneId": "f1d169df-e10e-451d-8481-0d0290b7cbbe",
    "propId": "3df5b8ad-e63f-47ab-bc12-c0cd93af40e6",
    "actorId": null,
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.interact",
        "name": "Interact"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "17de8184-8d8e-42d6-b748-9029f2cdad29",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "bb6e1f5f-f421-486a-9020-a3032d525bdd",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "edf46436-7072-40a2-8cbe-d20854bc5b03",
                            "text": "Look at the Statue",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.showCloseUp",
                                    "imageName": "ShadowStatueCU.png"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "c0480b68-8987-4df7-8c17-a9869ed3a86b",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Looks like a statue of a Wizard using his staff as a weapon. He looks rather tough. I wouldn't want to mess with him in real life.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "01060b1e-3424-4f30-80db-07074cbb6132",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "There's a large plaque at the bottom of the statue...",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "89060888-5f5c-494b-bd96-026d972b6dae",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "\"Legend states that Shadow was not seen or heard. Shadow would appear and strike with fierce intensity then disappear. No one knows of Shadow's whereabouts, so Shadow still might still be at large or buried underground. Either way, Shadow met his objectives each and every time.\"",
                                    "emotion": "4",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "e48ce657-dc09-4430-a7d3-9c817b373253",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "That's the way to do it! Pop in, take everyone by surprise, pepper 'em with spells, and pop somewhere else! Why does anyone even bother with hand-to-hand combat?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7a469f19-bd59-4400-8a68-ca9f72bbb1c4",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Of course, you've got to be as fast and focused as someone like Shadow, or you could pop into a boulder or something. Or with your back turned to some drooling nightmare, takes your head off in half a second. So I guess that's why it's not for everyone.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "9c78374b-d552-4db7-a797-9f49af591c7e",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "And I know capes are traditional, but if I was a Wizard, I don't think I'd ever wear one. Don't they get in the way of your staff and your wand? What are they, just for dramatic effect?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "45ad8658-c204-42e2-b122-51047d50a82f",
                            "text": "Move the Statue",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.playAnimation",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "animationName": "ReachOut",
                                    "wait": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "5071b562-1c00-48cc-b645-7cbf918b57a0",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Oofda! It weighs more than a Manticore!",
                                    "emotion": "4",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f2d97662-d68b-4b34-b57e-a1d313064aa0",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Not that I've ever picked up a Manticore.",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "6cc5db9f-5a1d-4459-ab66-7b5117f57206",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Or know what it really is. But I'll bet it's not as heavy as this statue.",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "acc318ab-0c9a-4f0b-8c18-5493d76ef131",
                            "text": "Steal the Statue",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "0e07fa23-07b5-43a3-a25e-10f75951f9ea",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Oh, no. Not a chance. Shadow could be watching me right now. In fact, he could BE this statue. Nobody knows for sure.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "1c237086-4e7f-49bc-8563-d63c2094c435",
                            "text": "Sense Magic on the Statue",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.hideCloseUp",
                                    "waitForSeconds": 1
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                    "id": "9cfb6390-843f-48c7-92ea-6c58f26eda66",
                                    "scriptId": "533e1ce1-13d3-439f-8544-dbdf808d30c4",
                                    "entryPointId": "17de8184-8d8e-42d6-b748-9029f2cdad29",
                                    "currentScope": "Scenes",
                                    "currentSceneId": "5f4c53b2-540d-4627-af71-7ede35c6d84b",
                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                    "currentPropId": null
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "72dfc5ad-b428-4b91-bd0a-c5aa75dcd89b",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "I may not be able to detect any magic on this statue, but given that it's about the mysterious Shadow, it's entirely possible that it's magical on some level I can't even sense.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
